atio between two given colors meets the 3:1 requirement","type":"text"}],"role":"symbol","fragments":[{"text":"var","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"meets3to1","kind":"identifier"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"preciseIdentifier":"s:Sb","text":"Bool","kind":"typeIdentifier"}],"kind":"symbol","url":"\/documentation\/oudsfoundations\/oudswcag21ratio\/meets3to1","type":"topic","identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSFoundations\/documentation\/OUDSFoundations\/OUDSWCAG21Ratio\/meets3to1","title":"meets3to1"},"ic_layers.png":{"variants":[{"traits":["1x","light"],"url":"\/images\/OUDSFoundations\/ic_layers.png"}],"alt":null,"identifier":"ic_layers.png","type":"image"},"doc://OUDSFoundations/documentation/OUDSFoundations/OUDSWCAG21Ratio":{"abstract":[{"text":"Some countries set up new laws so as to force companies to have a better accessibility of their digital services.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"This is for example the case for France with the ","type":"text"},{"isActive":true,"identifier":"https:\/\/accessibilite.numerique.gouv.fr","type":"reference"},{"text":",","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"also named “RGAA”.","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"The WCAG specifications, for AA level, defines a contrast ratio of 4.5:1 for textual elements (i.e. texts), and 3:1 for non-textual elements (i.e. link’s chevron)."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"However it is higly recommended for mobile devices to reach AAA level because of the screen sizes and luminosity issues, i.e. 7:1 for textual"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"and 4.5:1 for non-textual elements."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"This utility helps to define whether a set of contrast ratio matches AA and AAA or not."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"See for example "},{"isActive":true,"identifier":"https:\/\/system.design.orange.com\/0c1af118d\/p\/2531b9-accessibility-compliance","type":"reference"}],"role":"symbol","fragments":[{"text":"struct","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"OUDSWCAG21Ratio","kind":"identifier"}],"kind":"symbol","navigatorTitle":[{"text":"OUDSWCAG21Ratio","kind":"identifier"}],"url":"\/documentation\/oudsfoundations\/oudswcag21ratio","type":"topic","identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSFoundations\/documentation\/OUDSFoundations\/OUDSWCAG21Ratio","title":"OUDSWCAG21Ratio"},"https://system.design.orange.com/0c1af118d/p/2531b9-accessibility-compliance":{"url":"https:\/\/system.design.orange.com\/0c1af118d\/p\/2531b9-accessibility-compliance","titleInlineContent":[{"text":"the following guidelines","type":"text"}],"identifier":"https:\/\/system.design.orange.com\/0c1af118d\/p\/2531b9-accessibility-compliance","type":"link","title":"the following guidelines"},"https://accessibilite.numerique.gouv.fr":{"url":"https:\/\/accessibilite.numerique.gouv.fr","titleInlineContent":[{"text":"Référentiel Général d’Amélioration de l’Accessibilité","type":"text"}],"identifier":"https:\/\/accessibilite.numerique.gouv.fr","type":"link","title":"Référentiel Général d’Amélioration de l’Accessibilité"}}}